Use the standard library
This is how to smallest_change of arr:
  Remember that changes is 0
  Remember that left is 0
  Remember that right is diff of arr's length and 1
  Do this arr's length times:
    When left is at least right, then:
      Leave the loop
    End when
    When item left in arr is not item right in arr, then:
      Increase changes by 1
    End when
    Increase left by 1
    Decrease right by 1
  End do
  The answer is changes
